About: gg_outlined_v2
Focused around one large building, a path around to each spawn blocked by a wall you must climb. Two ladders go straight to the top floor but place you out in the open. A Ramp on either side also makes a path to the top. 4 small bunker/buildings are positioned in a cross atop. Inside the main building is a block with paths each way around it and over it. There is a hole in the ceiling to allow dropping down to the bottom floor. Can also be used for knife arena if you don't think its to big, no buyzone.

Credits: Still, i made this map but i give credit to
